Token.Abstract: The SPOfferWallViewControllerDelegate protocol is to be implemented by classes that wish to be notified when a presented SPOfferWallViewControllerDelegate is dismissed.

Sent when the SPOfferWallViewController finished. It can have been explicitly dismissed by the user, closed itself when redirecting outside of the app to proceed with an offer, or closed due to an error.

Parameter.Name: offerWallVC
Parameter.Abstract: the SPOfferWallViewController which is being closed.

Parameter.Name: status
Parameter.Abstract: if there was a network error, this will have the value of SPONSORPAYERRNETWORK.
